original_title: Richmond: St. Marks Place - Nicholas Street
text:
(1)
St. Marks Place, north side, at Nicholas Street,
showing the Wisteria Apartments (at No. 141) and the Castleton Apartments.
March 22, 1930

P. L. Sperr

(2)
The same, another view, as seen from the Curtis
High School grounds.
March 5, 1930

P. L. Sperr
